        "execSummary":  "Anthropic is proactively engaging the public on AI\u0027s most contentious societal questions ΓÇö jobs, family, and scientific progress ΓÇö in a move that blends stakeholder transparency with reputation management ahead of expected regulatory pressure. For enterprise leaders, this signals that even frontier AI labs are acknowledging legitimacy concerns that employees, regulators, and customers are already raising internally. Organizations deploying AI at scale should anticipate that these same questions will surface in workforce communications and public-facing disclosures. The key caveat: a commitment to publicly track responses is meaningful only if the follow-through is substantive rather than performative.",
